Biography

Summary

Philip Dionisius was born in Vaaloria, where he lived most of his young life. Still in a young age he got involved in politics and was nominated a Count after a few years and sent to govern the distant city of Nehlya, so Vaaloria could have a closer control on the city. With the funds from Vaaloria, young Philip made the small town a big and prosperous city. Being at a such long distance from the actual kingdom on the continent, slowly Count Dionisius slipped away from control as he created new trade routes, trained Nehlya's own army and built the city's own academies.

Today he is the governor of the Independent City of Nehlya.
